Introduction

Yunah is a South Korean singer and dancer under Belift Lab. She is the leader and lead vocalist of the South Korean girl group ILLIT.

In June 2023, she participated in HYBE and Belift Lab's survival show called R U Next?, where she was chosen by the label to be the sixth member to debut in the final group ILLIT.
